lead_paragraph: New England manager Sam Allardyce has admitted that he will be nervous when he leads the national side out for the first time in their opening 2018 World Cup qualifier against Slovakia on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Allardyce Admits to England Nerves Ahead of Slovakia Game
